text: Aleksandr Arkadyevich Zakarlyuka (; born 24 June 1995) is a Russian football forward. He plays in Estonia for Narva Trans. ==Club career== He made his professional debut in the Russian Professional Football League for FC Zenit-2 St. Petersburg on 15 July 2013 in a game against FC Tosno.
